Dr. {last_name},

{volume_hook}, I wanted to put two products in front of you that have been gaining traction with ortho practices in your MAC jurisdiction.

1. ProPacks - standardized post-op incision care kits built for {procedure_focus} cases. Better outcomes, less physician time on wound management, cleaner audit trail, and stronger per-case economics than the typical piecemeal approach.

2. Microlyte SAM - an advanced antimicrobial wound matrix (HCPCS A2005). Fully synthetic and bioresorbable, ionic/metallic silver that delivers 99.99% microbial reduction for 72+ hours, and a 'peel and place' application with no painful removal. Because your practice falls in a non-LCD MAC jurisdiction, Day 1 post-op use is supported without a 30-day conservative care failure requirement.

Worth a 15-minute intro call, or a lunch & learn at your {city} office? Happy to bring samples of both and the HCPCS / coverage paperwork.

Best,
